/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/building_models/current_hunts/big-thinkers/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/exact-ns-no-near-closed-tao-circuit/planning-runs/run-001/refined/chain-03.md:5:The constructive search route is worth keeping, but only if it stops optimizing an ad hoc "Tao-likeness" surrogate and instead searches within a fixed exact admissibility framework. The goal is to find the smallest honest exact packet class that survives exact closure and still shows meaningful Tao-like delayed transfer behavior, or else to produce a bounded diagnostic atlas of why such small packets fail.
