/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/building_models/current_hunts/big-thinkers/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-003/attacks/chain-01.md:15:The success metrics are derivative reduction, improved integrability, or local closure improvement on a named localized interaction. Those are exactly the currencies inherited from the same estimate architecture the mission context says is exhausted at the harmonic-analysis level.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/building_models/current_hunts/big-thinkers/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-003/attacks/chain-01.md:31:Step 3 is built to strip away gains that are "really" geometric or pressure-tensor effects. That is good if the goal is a pure reformulation result. It is bad if the only real NS-specific cancellations are hybrid: exact algebraic form plus alignment, or rewrite plus concentrated tube geometry, or rewrite plus tensor structure. The chain risks discarding the only live mechanisms because they are not pure enough.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/building_models/current_hunts/big-thinkers/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-003/attacks/chain-01.md:41:The mission context already says the vorticity formulation also lands at the same `beta = 4/3` barrier, and that exact Beltrami cancellation evaporates under tiny perturbation. So some of the most natural Step 2 and Step 3 outputs are already strongly prefigured. The chain is at real risk of spending budget restating known negatives unless it says exactly what new localized estimate is being tested that prior work did not already rule out.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/building_models/current_hunts/big-thinkers/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-003/attacks/chain-01.md:52:- The allowed notions of gain are too heterogeneous. Derivative reduction, improved integrability, and "closure improvement" are different units. Without fixing the precise estimate and norm bookkeeping, Step 1 can compare incomparable effects and build a misleading shortlist.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/building_models/current_hunts/big-thinkers/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-003/attacks/chain-01.md:79:- "Survive modest perturbation away from special alignment" is not operationally defined. Perturbation in what norm, on what scale, and relative to which localization? A cancellation can look robust or fragile depending on the metric.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/building_models/current_hunts/big-thinkers/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-003/attacks/chain-01.md:94:- There is a risk of laundering a tiny local cancellation into a grand "attack path" with a huge unpriced gap between the estimate and the actual regularity mechanism.
